fields.Title: YARD / HANGED MAN BULLET
fields.Description:
This is the final phase of the hanged man:
1. White check to find bullet
2. Failure to find fridge
3. Bagging him and taking it away

fields.Title: Perception: "You touch the dead man's body. His..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You touch the dead man's body. His skin is cold, light blue and silvery in the light of the fridge. You *still* have no idea where to begin -- or what to even do with him...

fields.Title: Authority: "The word lingers in the air of the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The word lingers in the air of the basement, far away ice cream makers are buzzing and the sea wind blows outside...

fields.Title: Authority: "*Detective*."
fields.Dialogue Text: *Detective*.

fields.Title: You: "Crawl up his nostrils."
fields.Dialogue Text: Crawl up his nostrils.

fields.Title: Cuno: "Cuno is silent."
fields.Dialogue Text: Cuno is silent.

fields.Title: You: "Push deeper."
fields.Dialogue Text: Push deeper.

fields.Title: Empathy: "Quivering with awe."
fields.Dialogue Text: Quivering with awe.

fields.Title: You: ""Fucking shit.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fucking shit."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Yes. And the belt around his neck;..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes. And the belt around his neck; the hanging; even dragging him to the yard... *all* of it was done after this man was already dead."

fields.Title: You: ""I think I need to wash myself.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I think I need to wash myself."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""To hide something. The real killer..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "To hide something. The real killer? The real motivation? What really happened here."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Oh." He nods. "You *really, really..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh." He nods. "You *really, really* do. I am glad to hear you say that. Your room in the Whirling-in-Rags should come with a bathroom. Be sure to make use of it in the evening."

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""Fucking pig's probably thinking ab..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fucking pig's probably thinking about touching it again..."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""There is no need. We have been tho..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "There is no need. We have been thorough with the genitals..." The lieutenant looks worried.

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "His fingernails have turned dark. T..."
fields.Dialogue Text: His fingernails have turned dark. They're chipped and quite long. There is dirt under them. That's all.
fields.Alternate1: His fingernails have turned dark. They're chipped, and quite long. There is dirt under them. Surprise-surprise. No bullet here.

fields.Title: Authority: "It seems he is leaving you no choic..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It seems he is leaving you no choice in the matter.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Klaasje told us the bullet hit him..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Klaasje told us the bullet hit him in the *mouth* -- try putting your hand there..."

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "The lieutenant should *clearly* be..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant should *clearly* be here for this. You're lost.

fields.Title: You: "Bag the corpse and drag it to the m..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Bag the corpse and drag it to the motor carriage. [Leave.]

fields.Title: You: "Feel around first."
fields.Dialogue Text: Feel around first.

fields.Title: Interfacing: "You're not far, it'll come to you,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You're not far, it'll come to you, keep crawling...

fields.Title: You: ""I can't get it...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I can't get it..."

fields.Title: You: ""Can I have it?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Can I have it?"

fields.Title: You: ""Agreed.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Agreed."

fields.Title: You: ""The ligament mark, the fractured h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The ligament mark, the fractured hyoid bone, it was all treatment..."

fields.Title: You: ""What happens next?" (Proceed.)"
fields.Dialogue Text: "What happens next?" (Proceed.)

fields.Title: Cuno: ""I can't believe the pig is strokin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I can't believe the pig is stroking him *again*..."

fields.Title: You: ""I've got a gut feeling that there'..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I've got a gut feeling that there's more to this corpse."

fields.Title: You: ""Can't he just... hang out here for..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Can't he just... hang out here for a while longer?"

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "The inside of the head feels cold a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The inside of the head feels cold and smooth like a glove as you pull out, sweat dripping down your brow -- careful not to lose the prize between your fingers...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Only if *all else* fails," he stre..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Only if *all else* fails," he stresses.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""We bag the corpse and carry him to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We bag the corpse and carry him to the holding pen of my Kineema. I can transport him to Processing myself, but I *will* be gone for the rest of the day."

fields.Title: Interfacing: "Oh well -- in another lifetime."
fields.Dialogue Text: Oh well -- in another lifetime.

fields.Title: Tutorial Agent: "If you have nothing to do, read boo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: If you have nothing to do, read books or sit on the bench on the plaza.

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "We didn't fall for it, he thinks. T..."
fields.Dialogue Text: We didn't fall for it, he thinks. There's pride in there.

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "There go those beautiful enamel boo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There go those beautiful enamel boots. You will never own the full set now. May they rest in Processing...

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "A vision of black and dark red deat..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A vision of black and dark red death, pried open by your naked hands and studded with teeth. Looks like he's laughing, death fumes rising from the throat. And there, in the back of his mouth, above the bell of the uvula, right in the soft palate...
fields.Alternate1: A vision of black and dark red death: pried open by your hands and studded with teeth. Looks like he's laughing, death fumes rising from his throat. And there, in the back of his mouth, above the bell of the uvula, right in the soft palate...

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "Your fingers are all the way in now..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Your fingers are all the way in now, reaching toward the inside of his skull. The cavity goes further, but the entry wound isn't wide enough for the rest of your hand to follow...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Can you... can you get to it?" He..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Can you... can you get to it?" He searches his pockets for something.

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "There's a tiny crack, a protrusion..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There's a tiny crack, a protrusion in the cranium, right in the back of his head. Your finger must be pointing straight at it. From the *inside*.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""F****ts can't get enough of that d..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "F****ts can't get enough of that dick..."

fields.Title: Jump to: [Perception: "Your arm reaches out and your eyes..."]
Kim Kitsuragi: "He unrolls the plastic. "I need a l..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He unrolls the plastic. "I need a little help for carrying him to the holding pen of my Kineema. I'll take it from there."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "He closes his notebook and cracks h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He closes his notebook and cracks his neck. "Let's move. With every hour, whatever we're looking for in the deceased will become harder to find."

fields.Title: Jump to: [ICE BEAR FRIDGE MAIN HUB]
Tutorial Agent: "If you have nothing to do, read boo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: If you have nothing to do, read books or sit on the bench on the plaza.

fields.Title: You: "What is this?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What is this?
fields.Sequence: TravelTo(Tequila Sunset, autopsy_TeqLoc); PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, body_inspect)@2; HideActualHeld()@2;
fields.Alternate1: "Here we go."

fields.Title: You: "Play with it -- this feels right."
fields.Dialogue Text: Play with it -- this feels right.

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "A black trickle of liquid runs into..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A black trickle of liquid runs into his throat from the wound...

fields.Title: You: "Put your finger in."
fields.Dialogue Text: Put your finger in.

fields.Title: Perception: "Sharp, serrated material. The edges..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Sharp, serrated material. The edges cut right into your skin.
fields.Alternate1: Sharp, serrated material. The edges cut right into your skin. This must be the *bullet*.
fields.Alternate2: Ice cold, serrated metal. Its edges cut right through the latex and into your finger.

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "The cartilage gives in with a crack..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The cartilage gives in with a crack, like some fruit. Just like that your hand is in his head. Strange fluid streams down your wrist -- and then you feel it, with the tip of your finger...
fields.Alternate1: The cartilage gives in with a crack, like some fruit. Just like that your hand is in his head. Fluid streams down your wrist -- and then you finally feel it, with the tip of your finger...

fields.Title: Suggestion: "Her voice is absolutely sizzling wi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Her voice is absolutely sizzling with excitement.

fields.Title: You: "Slowly pull your fingers out..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Slowly pull your fingers out...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "With a *crack* he punches the knife..."
fields.Dialogue Text: With a *crack* he punches the knife in the skull. Then one more time -- and one more -- until the bone comes loose like eggshell. Inside you feel the jelly move from his poking. The object is still under your finger.
fields.Alternate1: With a *crack* he punches the knife in the skull. Then one more time -- and one more -- until the bone comes loose like eggshell. Inside you feel the jello move from his poking. The bullet is still under your finger.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""We need to add an item to the inju..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We need to add an item to the injury list." He turns to his notebook. "Injury #4: Oval entry wound with an abrasion collar. Soft palate, back of mouth."
fields.Alternate1: "Looks like we need to add one more item to your injury list..." He takes out his notebook, *click* goes the pen. "Injury #4. Oval entry wound with an abrasion collar. Soft palate, back of mouth."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Good-good..." The fridge in the ba..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Good-good..." The fridge in the background buzzes with excitement.

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "Suddenly, you recall: Two officers..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Suddenly, you recall: Two officers must be present for a field autopsy. You take your hand from the dead man's face and open your eyes. You will still need to come back with the lieutenant.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""...*this* injury here." He points..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "...*this* injury here." He points to the mark encircling the corpse's neck.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I have had this doubt since I insp..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I have had this doubt since I inspected his hands, officer -- there were no signs of struggle. No claw marks on his neck. Why? Why didn't he fight for his life?"
fields.Alternate1: "I've had this doubt since you showed me the tracks, officer. We could not account for why they *carried* him over -- why not march him? There was no satisfying explanation."
fields.Alternate2: "I've had this doubt since you pointed out the lividity was faint. They know we do it -- analyze hypostasis. I have had perpetrators manipulate the body position before."
fields.Alternate3: "I've had this doubt since you had your *hunch*, officer. That he was doing something *else* at the time of his death. I don't have that kind of intuition myself -- and I don't usually trust it. But it made me... doubt."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""To put him out of his misery?" He..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "To put him out of his misery?" He thinks. "It's possible, but it does not explain all the other dubious things here -- lack of struggle primarily. I may be intellectually sloppy, but I prefer one theory at a time. And this just smacks of treatment to me."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Hey..." A wide smile appears on hi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Hey..." A wide smile appears on his face. "Wasn't there a *giant ice bear sarcophagus* below that building?" He points toward the commercial area.

fields.Title: Endurance: "Soon you'll be looking for clues in..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Soon you'll be looking for clues in a pile of sludge and bones.

fields.Title: Tutorial Agent: "This means Lieutenant Kitsuragi wil..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This means Lieutenant Kitsuragi will leave the party until tomorrow morning. You're free to do side-tasks and even the main case -- though it might be more difficult.

fields.Title: You: "Brain stem?"
fields.Dialogue Text: Brain stem?

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Work on the case, tend to personal..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Work on the case, tend to personal matters? Try not to do anything *too* dangerous. An officer needs backup in a neighbourhood like this."

fields.Title: Jump to: [You: "Touch it with your finger, gently...."]
You: "No, this is too much. (Pull your ha..."
fields.Dialogue Text: No, this is too much. (Pull your hand out.)

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "The pain is barely noticeable under..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The pain is barely noticeable under the adrenaline rush.

fields.Title: You: "Inspect the skull first."
fields.Dialogue Text: Inspect the skull first.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Unknown calibre. Rifled. Some kind..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Unknown calibre. Rifled. Some kind of brittle alloy, fractured on impact..."

fields.Title: You: "Say nothing, just nod."
fields.Dialogue Text: Say nothing, just nod.

fields.Title: You: ""Dead, daba-doop-doop.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Dead, daba-doop-doop."

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "You pull down his breeches. Marblin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You pull down his breeches. Marbling is present around the crotch. The penis has shrunk, crawling half way back inside him. There is nothing mysterious or noteworthy here.
fields.Alternate1: The genitals in his breeches continue to be unnoteworthy -- you see the penis of a dead man. If you've seen it once, you already got the picture.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Mhm." He gets up. "This is one tas..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Mhm." He gets up. "This is one task we *cannot* sideline. With every hour, whatever we're looking for will become harder to find."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "He frowns, thinking. "Try putting y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He frowns, thinking. "Try putting your hand in his mouth and probing for the bullet in his *head*."

fields.Title: You: "Bag the corpse and drag it to the m..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Bag the corpse and drag it to the motor carriage. [Leave.]

fields.Title: You: "Fish it out."
fields.Dialogue Text: Fish it out.
fields.Sequence: PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, bullet_F); PlayAnimation(The Hanged Man, bullet_F);

fields.Title: Perception: "Your arm reaches out and your eyes..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Your arm reaches out and your eyes close, as if by their own volition. It's dark all around. You feel cold, slippery flesh -- first with your fingertips, then under the palm of your hand.
fields.Alternate1: Your arm reaches out and your eyes close -- as if by their own volition. It's dark all around. You feel cold, dead flesh through the latex glove. It's right under the palm of your hand.

fields.Title: Perception: "...you see a hole, barely visible t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: ...you see a hole, barely visible to the human eye. It is swollen shut, almost vanished, no larger than 0.4 cm in radius. The edges appear darkened.

fields.Title: Cuno: "Cuno nods too. He takes a step clos..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Cuno nods too. He takes a step closer.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The lieutenant answers with the sou..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant answers with the sound of his pen on paper.

fields.Title: Jump to: [Interfacing: "You're not far, it'll come to you,..."]
You: ""Keep it, lieutenant. As a gift.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Keep it, lieutenant. As a gift."

fields.Title: You: "Look in his pants again."
fields.Dialogue Text: Look in his pants again.

fields.Title: You: "Give up."
fields.Dialogue Text: Give up.

fields.Title: You: ""No, let's just leave it to the Pro..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No, let's just leave it to the Processing guys."

fields.Title: Authority: "Not to mention the damage that woul..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Not to mention the damage that would be dealt to the force's reputation by the corpse just rotting here like this...

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "The *funk soul brother* at the back..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The *funk soul brother* at the back of his head has gone dark. Forever.

fields.Title: You: "Pull your fingers back and nod."
fields.Dialogue Text: Pull your fingers back and nod.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""A bullet." The lieutenant picks it..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "A bullet." The lieutenant picks it up between his fingers. "Unknown calibre. Rifled... you may remove your hand from the victim's head now, officer -- well done."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""No-no, you deserve it. We can log..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No-no, you deserve it. We can log it later." The lieutenant drops the bag in your bloody hand. It feels light.
fields.Alternate1: "No-no, you deserve it. We can log it later." The lieutenant drops the bag in your hand. It feels light.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""That was then. This time we have e..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "That was then. This time we have extensive tissue destruction away from the wound track. This time we have a *bullet*."

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""Fucking *beautiful...*""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fucking *beautiful...*"

fields.Title: You: "Don't touch it again."
fields.Dialogue Text: Don't touch it again.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""If you think so, officer." He nods..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "If you think so, officer." He nods. "I am not going to object."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Continue working here. The locals,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Continue working here. The locals, the case, or tend to your own business? I will meet you downstairs in the Whirling-in-Rags, tomorrow morning -- 7:30 sharp."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""All right." He takes out a shiny b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "All right." He takes out a shiny black body bag and starts pulling the plastic over the dead man's face.

fields.Title: Jump to: [ICE BEAR FRIDGE MAIN HUB]
Kim Kitsuragi: ""Yes -- now. I've rarely been disap..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes -- now. I've rarely been disappointed by the size of a *giant* ice bear fridge, but I think we should still take a look at it first. Make sure it's big *enough* before we carry him over."

fields.Title: Perception: "You really ought to wait until the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You really ought to wait until the cadaver is *refrigerated*. Digging around in this mess now is proving hopelessly difficult.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The lieutenant rubs his side for wa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant rubs his side for warmth. "It'll come to you sooner or later. At least he's safe here until then."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Work on the case, tend to personal..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Work on the case, tend to personal matters? Try not to do anything too dangerous. An officer needs backup in a neighbourhood like this."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""As I said, treatment is an attempt..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "As I said, treatment is an attempt to manipulate the body after death -- to hide the real cause with a *false* cause. In this case..."

fields.Title: Tutorial Agent: "This means Lieutenant Kitsuragi wil..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This means Lieutenant Kitsuragi will leave until tomorrow morning. Meanwhile, you're free to do side-tasks and even the main case -- though it might be more difficult.

fields.Title: You: "Open your eyes and look."
fields.Dialogue Text: Open your eyes and look.

fields.Title: You: "Fish it out."
fields.Dialogue Text: Fish it out.
fields.Sequence: PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, bullet_S); PlayAnimation(The Hanged Man, bullet_S);

fields.Title: You: "No. Touch something else."
fields.Dialogue Text: No. Touch something else.
fields.Sequence: PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, end); PlayAnimation(The Hanged Man, end);

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Okay, well... We're in livor morti..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay, well... We're in livor mortis here. He's disintegrating. We need to *refrigerate* the body, if we want to conduct another examination -- and we need to do it fast."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Okay." He unrolls the plastic. "I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay." He unrolls the plastic. "I need a little help for carrying him to the holding pen of my Kineema. I can take care of the rest."

fields.Title: You: ""An absolutely colossal fridge -- s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "An absolutely colossal fridge -- still plugged in -- *literally* in the shape of an ice bear!"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Now that's an overstatement. It's..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Now that's an overstatement. It's not actually *for* storing cadavers, or at least I hope so. I think we should take a look at it first. Make sure it's big *enough* before we carry him over."

fields.Title: Authority: "The word lingers in the air of the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The word lingers in the air of the yard, far away dogs are barking, further yet the sound of motor traffic...

fields.Title: Cuno: ""The fuck is he doing?" You hear a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The fuck is he doing?" You hear a voice squeak. It sounds very far away.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Fuckin' *CAVITY* C..." Cuno's voic..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fuckin' *CAVITY* C..." Cuno's voice is hushed.

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""Forget about the *fucking exit wou..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Forget about the *fucking exit wound*, bino! THE PIG IS WEARING HIM LIKE A FUCK PUPPET!"

fields.Title: Authority: "He's watching his old man get the b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He's watching his old man get the big prize at the claw game.

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "With a *plop*, your hand emerges fr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: With a *plop*, your hand emerges from the mouth, covered in blood up to the wrist. Between your fingers -- a small flower, a blossom made of lead!
fields.Alternate1: With a *plop*, your hand emerges from the mouth, covered in blood up to the wrist. Between your fingers -- a small flower, a blossom made of lead!
fields.Alternate2: With a *plop*, your hand emerges from the mouth. The garden glove is covered in blood right up to the wrist. Between your fingers -- a small flower, a blossom made of lead!

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "Out comes his small folding knife -..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Out comes his small folding knife -- the lieutenant moves its blade across the man's skull, searching for the exit wound...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Can you push it out?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Can you push it out?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""High velocity, temporary cavity in..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "High velocity, temporary cavity in brain tissue. Small exit wound on the occiput." He underlines the injury, forcefully. "How does that sound?"

fields.Title: You: ""Sounds like heaven.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sounds like heaven."

fields.Title: You: "Maybe if I touch it again..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Maybe if I touch it again...

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "The corpse seems to yawn contentedl..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The corpse seems to yawn contentedly, as though its glad you've run out of steam.

fields.Title: You: ""Okay -- where do we find a fridge..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay -- where do we find a fridge for the body?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""It would have to be *industrial* i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It would have to be *industrial* in size. Let's start by asking the proprietor of the Whirling-in-Rags, then the Frittte store down at the gates. And if neither has one..." His voice trails off -- and his gaze settles on *Cuno*.
fields.Alternate1: "It would have to be *industrial* in size. Let's start by asking Garte at the Whirling-in-Rags, and the Frittte store down at the gates. If they don't know..." His voice trails off -- and his gaze settles on *Cuno*. "But only if *all else* fails."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "He unrolls the plastic. "I need a l..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He unrolls the plastic. "I need a little help for carrying him to the holding pen of my Kineema. I'll take it from there."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""It's too late to take him into Pro..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's too late to take him into Processing today. I'll take him first thing tomorrow." He pulls the black plastic over the dead man's face.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Fuck are you looking at bino-man?..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fuck are you looking at bino-man? You wanna piece of the Cuno? Wanna get *fucked*?"

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "There go those beautiful enamel boo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There go those beautiful enamel boots. May they rest in Processing...

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "There go those beautiful enamel boo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There go those beautiful enamel boots. May they rest in Processing...

fields.Title: Hand/Eye Coordination: "This little thing could reveal much..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This little thing could reveal much about the weapon that shot it.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""All right." He takes out a shiny b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "All right." He takes out a shiny black body bag and starts pulling the plastic over the dead man's face.

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "Only the little one fits. The flesh..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Only the little one fits. The flesh changes shape as you bore in, searching for something in the cartilage.

fields.Title: You: "Touch it with your finger, gently...."
fields.Dialogue Text: Touch it with your finger, gently. (Proceed.)

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Mhm," he agrees. "Keep going.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Mhm," he agrees. "Keep going."

fields.Title: You: "Wriggle in..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Wriggle in...

fields.Title: Jump to: [Interfacing: "You're not far, it'll come to you,..."]
Cunoesse: ""What?! WHAT is it?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What?! WHAT is it?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""A bullet..." The lieutenant puts a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "A bullet..." The lieutenant puts a small bag marked *evidence* under it.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""There have been other signs too, s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "There have been other signs too, small things. We were right not to assign hanging as cause of death. As the perpetrators *expected* we would -- no such luck for them."

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "You can't shake the feeling that th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You can't shake the feeling that there are more secrets concealed in the flesh before you.

fields.Title: You: ""Correct.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Correct."

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "His brow furrows while his eyes gla..."
fields.Dialogue Text: His brow furrows while his eyes glaze over. The lieutenant looks regretful for not figuring this out before.

fields.Title: You: "What about that giant ice bear frid..."
fields.Dialogue Text: What about that giant ice bear fridge in the Doomed Commercial Area?

fields.Title: Jump to: [ICE BEAR FRIDGE MAIN HUB]
Kim Kitsuragi: ""All right." He takes out a shiny b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "All right." He takes out a shiny black body bag and starts pulling the plastic over the dead man's face.

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "We almost fell for it, he thinks. *..."
fields.Dialogue Text: We almost fell for it, he thinks. *Almost*.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I can drive him to Processing toda..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I can drive him to Processing today, no problem. Since we stalled with this... But this *does* mean I will be gone for the rest of the day."

fields.Title: You: "Push your fingers in his nose."
fields.Dialogue Text: Push your fingers in his nose.

fields.Title: You: "Touch something else."
fields.Dialogue Text: Touch something else.

fields.Title: Perception: "The thing you're looking for -- it'..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The thing you're looking for -- it's not there. Crawl out, spider...
fields.Alternate1: The thing you're looking for -- it's not here either. Crawl out, spider...

fields.Title: Cuno: ""My pig's fucking *got* it!""
fields.Dialogue Text: "My pig's fucking *got* it!"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Wait, detective!" Just as you star..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Wait, detective!" Just as you start to slide your fingers out...

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""Beautiful...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Beautiful..."

fields.Title: You: "Squeeze his nose."
fields.Dialogue Text: Squeeze his nose.

fields.Title: Interfacing: "This is the *irregularity* you felt..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is the *irregularity* you felt before. The one that was too tiny to register consciously.

fields.Title: Logic: "There is of course the very real po..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There is of course the very real possibility he was both shot *and* hanged.

fields.Title: Logic: "Hmm... Cuno looks like he gets arou..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Hmm... Cuno looks like he gets around. *Knows* Martinaise. And its fridges too probably...

fields.Title: You: ""What should I do in the meanwhile?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What should I do in the meanwhile?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Now, detective... I've rarely been..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Now, detective... I've rarely been disappointed by the size of a *giant* ice bear fridge, but I think we should still take a look at it first. Make sure it's big *enough* before we carry him over."

fields.Title: You: ""So that's what the *ice bear shape..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "So that's what the *ice bear shaped* refrigerator is for!"

fields.Title: Interfacing: "Oh well -- in another lifetime."
fields.Dialogue Text: Oh well -- in another lifetime.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I see it..." The lieutenant looks..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I see it..." The lieutenant looks in. There's a pen in his hand. His notebook is open at the red pages.
fields.Alternate1: "Abrasion collar..." The lieutenant looks in. There's a pen in his hand. His notebook is open at the copy paper.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Don't be silly." A smile comes acr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Don't be silly." A smile comes across his face. "You've earned it. Consider the binoclard episode forgotten." The lieutenant drops the bag in your bloody hand. It feels light.
fields.Alternate1: "Don't be silly." A smile comes across his face. "You've earned it. Consider the binoclard episode forgotten." He drops the bag in your hand.

fields.Title: You: ""God damn right.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "God damn right."

fields.Title: You: ""Treatment?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Treatment?"

fields.Title: You: ""Aren't we jumping to conclusions?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Aren't we jumping to conclusions?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Deadady-dead-dead.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Deadady-dead-dead."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I did not *just* come up with this..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I did not *just* come up with this. I've had my doubts since we found no signs of struggle on his wrists. No claw marks on his neck -- why? Why didn't he fight for his life?"
fields.Alternate1: "I did not *just* come up with this. I've had my doubts since you showed me the tracks, officer. Why did they *carry* him over -- why not march him? There is no satisfactory explanation."
fields.Alternate2: "I did not *just* come up with this. I've had my doubts since you said the lividity was faint. *They* know we do it -- analyze hypostasis. I have had perpetrators manipulate the body position before."
fields.Alternate3: "I did not *just* come up with this. I've had my doubts since you told me about that hunch, officer. Him doing something *else* when he died. I don't have intuition -- I don't usually trust it. But it made me doubt."

fields.Title: You: ""Who would do this?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Who would do this?"

fields.Title: You: "Look under his fingernails, like Ki..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Look under his fingernails, like Kim already did.

fields.Title: You: ""Yes. There's something we're not s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes. There's something we're not seeing."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "He shakes his head. "I worked as on..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He shakes his head. "I worked as one of these *Processing guys* for a year. They are butchers and clowns. I once saw twenty CODs go misidentified in one week. Chances are slim to none that they'll find anything useful in processing."

fields.Title: You: ""Then what?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Then what?"

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "You can almost see the body decompo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You can almost see the body decomposing before your very eyes. You should drop everything else and look for a way to preserve it so you can conduct your examination better.

fields.Title: You: ""I need to take another look at the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I need to take another look at the body first."

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "Yes. That's what this part is calle..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Yes. That's what this part is called.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""We put him in a bag and carry him..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We put him in a bag and carry him to the holding pen of my Kineema. The bodybag should contain the odour for the duration of the transport..."

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "His face. His cheeks, his nose, his..."
fields.Dialogue Text: His face. His cheeks, his nose, his fat swollen lips. Like a spider, your hand crawls over his features. Everything is silent.
fields.Alternate1: His face. His cheeks, his nose, his fat swollen lips. Like a rubber spider your gloved hand crawls on his features. Everything is silent all around.

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "They are swollen shut -- you need t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: They are swollen shut -- you need to really *push* to get in.

fields.Title: Jump to: [You: "Touch it with your finger, gently...."]
You: "Punch a hole through his mouth."
fields.Dialogue Text: Punch a hole through his mouth.

fields.Title: Interfacing: "You push your hand further in. What..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You push your hand further in. Whatever is in there keeps rolling between your fingers as you beckon it to come out.
fields.Alternate1: You push your hand further in. The bullet keeps rolling between your fingers as you beckon it to come out.

fields.Title: You: "Drop it in."
fields.Dialogue Text: Drop it in.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Of course. You've *earned* it." Th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Of course. You've *earned* it." The lieutenant drops the bag in your bloody hand. It feels light.
fields.Alternate1: "Of course. You deserve it." The lieutenant drops the bag in your hand. It feels light.

fields.Title: You: ""Sounds about right.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sounds about right."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""There have been other signs too, s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "There have been other signs too, small details. Everything is too neatly designed for us to assign probable cause here. As we did, foolhardily. Well -- no more."

fields.Title: Logic: "Or -- remember the buttons on that..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Or -- remember the buttons on that intercom over there, on the side of the building next to the Whirling? One was for "Revachol *Ice* City"? Perhaps it's a... clue?

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""All right." He takes out a shiny b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "All right." He takes out a shiny black body bag and starts pulling the plastic over the dead man's face.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Hurry. This is one task we *cannot..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Hurry. This is one task we *cannot* sideline. With every hour, whatever we're looking for will become harder to find."

fields.Title: Jump to: [Authority: "It seems he is leaving you no choic..."]
Inland Empire: "You're on the right track."
fields.Dialogue Text: You're on the right track.

fields.Title: Encyclopedia: "This is what he used to regulate hi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is what he used to regulate his emotions with...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""One more thing -- this was *really..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "One more thing -- this was *really* good work, detective."

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "The tongue moves freely in the cavi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The tongue moves freely in the cavity. The mucous of the mouth is slippery, delicate to touch. From the soft meat -- teeth are budding; hard pearls of bone in the gums. And in the back of the mouth...
fields.Alternate1: The tongue moves freely in the cavity. The mucose of the mouth is slippery, fragile even through the latex. From the soft meat -- teeth are budding; hard pearls of bone in the gums. And in the back of the mouth...

fields.Title: Visual Calculus: "An *abrasion collar*! THIS is what..."
fields.Dialogue Text: An *abrasion collar*! THIS is what we're after.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Oh shit, C...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh shit, C..."

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "The basal ganglia feels clumpy -- w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The basal ganglia feels clumpy -- what entered here has torn apart his reptilian complex.
fields.Alternate1: The basal ganglia feels clumpy -- the bullet has torn apart his reptilian complex.

fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "All the muscles in your body harden..."
fields.Dialogue Text: All the muscles in your body harden. Time to *enter* him.

fields.Title: Perception: "Can you feel it? You're so close! R..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Can you feel it? You're so close! Rip his jaws open now, look in...

fields.Title: You: ""A little help, lieutenant?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "A little help, lieutenant?"

fields.Title: Visual Calculus: "The object that is in there stopped..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The object that is in there stopped just short of the skull, in the encephalus, knocking this tiny fracture into the cranium...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Do you think we missed something?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Do you think we missed something?"

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "You can almost see the body decompo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You can almost see the body decomposing before your very eyes. You should drop everything else and look for a way to preserve it so you can conduct your examination better.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "He nods. "I had my doubts --  there..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He nods. "I had my doubts --  there were no signs of a struggle on his hands. No claw marks on his neck. But still..."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Yes. We should take a closer look..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes. We should take a closer look at it. I am certain it has more to tell us."

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "The corpse looks *enormous* with it..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The corpse looks *enormous* with its bloated belly. Was the ice bear fridge really that giant? You should go and measure it, just to be sure.

fields.Title: Authority: "*Detective*."
fields.Dialogue Text: *Detective*.

fields.Title: Authority: "The word lingers in the air of the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The word lingers in the air of the yard, as far away dogs are barking, further yet the sound of motor traffic...

fields.Title: Authority: "The word lingers in the air of base..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The word lingers in the air of basement, far away ice cream makers are buzzing and the sea wind blows outside...

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "The oral cavity is cold and moist...."
fields.Dialogue Text: The oral cavity is cold and moist. A ball-like tongue attaches itself to the base of the mouth, lolling around like a scallop...

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""The fuck is happening?!""
fields.Dialogue Text: "The fuck is happening?!"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""We have the makings of a... very s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We have the makings of a... very small exit wound here." The lieutenant leans closer.

fields.Title: You: "Whisper: "I got it.""
fields.Dialogue Text: Whisper: "I got it."

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "A small flower of metal blossoms fr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A small flower of metal blossoms from the man's head, followed by your finger.
fields.Alternate1: A fractured piece of lead, like a flower, blossoms from the man's head -- followed by your finger.
fields.Alternate2: A small flower of metal blossoms from the man's head, followed by your yellow finger.

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "You pick it between your fingers. T..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You pick it between your fingers. The mass feels large, very porous somehow. Keep crawling, lest you break it...
fields.Alternate1: You pick it between your fingers. The mass is even larger than *your* nose. Very *porous* somehow. Like it's about to pop. Keep crawling, lest you break it.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""That's for us to find out. But *th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "That's for us to find out. But *this* -- it will make finding them just a little easier."

fields.Title: Jump to: [Kim Kitsuragi: ""Do you think we missed something?""]
You: ""We should have known.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "We should have known."

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "Meanwhile, the lieutenant is sittin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Meanwhile, the lieutenant is sitting behind his desk, hunched over a stack of paperwork. His help would be invaluable right now.

fields.Title: Jump to: [ICE BEAR FRIDGE MAIN HUB]
Inland Empire: "The ululations of the limbic system..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The ululations of the limbic system have ended. All is quiet.

fields.Title: Authority: "*Detective*."
fields.Dialogue Text: *Detective*.

fields.Title: Perception: "You run your hands over the victim'..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You run your hands over the victim's cold body: his limbs, his torso with its swollen organs... maybe you should be more *thorough*?
fields.Alternate1: You run your  hands over the cold-cold body of the victim: his limbs, swollen organs... there's a bullet in here, somewhere.

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "Your index fits right in there. A t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Your index fits right in there. A tight tunnel of flesh opens up -- tissue damage -- wide enough for two fingers. As you push both in, you reach through his mouth, right into his brain stem.

fields.Title: You: "Push deeper."
fields.Dialogue Text: Push deeper.

fields.Title: You: ""I feel a solid object, right under..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I feel a solid object, right under the skull."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Here's your prize." He drops the b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Here's your prize." He drops the bullet in an evidence bag and puts it in your hand -- your other hand, the one *not* covered in blood and cerebral cortex.
fields.Alternate1: "Here's your prize." He drops the bullet in an evidence bag and puts it in your hand. It feels light.

fields.Title: You: ""Keep it, lieutenant. Also, I'm sor..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Keep it, lieutenant. Also, I'm sorry for calling you a binoclard."

fields.Title: You: ""I'm *still* not sure." (Look at yo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm *still* not sure." (Look at your hand, quizzically.)

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Treatment, officer, is an attempt..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Treatment, officer, is an attempt to manipulate the body after death -- to hide the real cause with a *false* cause. In this case..."

fields.Title: You: ""Maybe the bullet holds more answer..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Maybe the bullet holds more answers?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""If you want for this task to slowl..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "If you want for this task to slowly become impossible, then yes. Otherwise -- no. He's been *hanging out* far too long already. We need to ice him."

fields.Title: You: ""This concurs with the Hardie boys..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "This concurs with the Hardie boys story."
fields.Alternate1: "This concurs with the Hardie boys story -- and Klaasje's."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""If the Hardies are to be trusted,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "If the Hardies are to be trusted, there should be a bullet in there..." The lieutenant looks at you. "Try putting your hand in his mouth and probing for the bullet in his head."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I will need a little help carrying..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I will need a little help carrying him -- you take the hands, I'll take the legs."

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "Your fingers slide into the remains..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Your fingers slide into the remains of his limbic system. There is no resistance. It's gelatinous. The slug-like structures are damaged too, the tearing extends deep into both hemispheres.
fields.Alternate1: Your yellow fingers slide into the remains of the limbic system. There is no resistance. Its gelatinous. The slug-like structures are damaged too, the tearing extends deep into both hemispheres.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Mhm. Withdraw your hand 4 centimet..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Mhm. Withdraw your hand 4 centimetres please."

fields.Title: You: ""There." (Nod toward the protrusion..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "There." (Nod toward the protrusion.)

fields.Title: You: "Push."
fields.Dialogue Text: Push.

fields.Title: Jump to: [Kim Kitsuragi: "Out comes his small folding knife -..."]
You: ""You think so?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You think so?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I have had my doubts for a while n..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I have had my doubts for a while now. Since I saw there were no signs of struggle on his hands. And no claw marks on his neck..."
fields.Alternate1: "I have had my doubts since you showed me the tracks. Why did they *carry* him over -- why not march him, I thought. There was no satisfying explanation."
fields.Alternate2: "I have had my doubts since you pointed out the lividity was faint. They know we analyze hypostasis. I have had perpetrators manipulate the body position before."
fields.Alternate3: "I have had my doubts about this since you told me he was doing something *else*. At the time of his death. I don't have that kind of intuition -- I don't usually trust it. But it made me... doubt."

fields.Title: You: ""Maybe they just shot him *while* t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Maybe they just shot him *while* they hanged him?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""And, if we are to believe Hardie b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "And, if we are to believe Hardie boys, it's somewhere in there..."

fields.Title: You: ""But where?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "But where?"

fields.Title: Jump to: [ICE BEAR FRIDGE MAIN HUB]
Half Light: "Why yes there was. It was massive...."
fields.Dialogue Text: Why yes there was. It was massive. Red eyes glowing in the dark.

fields.Title: You: ""You'll be gone? What should I do i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You'll be gone? What should I do in the meanwhile?"

fields.Title: You: ""You'll be gone? What should I do i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You'll be gone? What should I do in the meanwhile?"

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "There go those beautiful enamel boo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There go those beautiful enamel boots. You will never own the full set now. May they rest in Processing...

fields.Title: You: "Put your fingers in his mouth."
fields.Dialogue Text: Put your fingers in his mouth.
fields.Sequence: PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, body_enter); PlayAnimation(The Hanged Man, body_enter);

fields.Title: Interfacing: "You pick the object between your in..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You pick the object between your index and middle finger. It feels sharp, like metal. With your face twisting from pain and concentration, all you need to do is just...
fields.Alternate1: You pick the sharp, metal bullet between your index and middle finger. With your face twisting from pain and concentration, all you need to do is just...
fields.Alternate2: You pick the object between your index and middle finger. Feels sharp, like metal. You press your teeth together, your jaw is clenched. All you need to do is just...

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Oh yeah...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh yeah..."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Opinion -- fatal injury.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Opinion -- fatal injury."

fields.Title: You: ""Wasn't that what we thought the la..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Wasn't that what we thought the last time?" (Clean your hand in the snow.)
fields.Alternate1: "Wasn't that what we thought the last time?"
fields.Alternate2: "Wasn't that what we thought the last time?" (Shake the gloves clean.)
fields.Alternate3: "Wasn't that what we thought the last time?" (Clean your hand in the handkerchief.)

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""We have *extensive* tissue destruc..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We have *extensive* tissue destruction away from the wound track -- we have a *bullet*."

fields.Title: Logic: "He's proposing the bullet was the r..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He's proposing the bullet was the real cause of death -- and the hanging an attempt to *conceal* this fact.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""In short, you and I are the *last*..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "In short, you and I are the *last* line of detection. If you're not sure we got everything, we need to look *again*. And for that -- we need to refrigerate the corpse."

fields.Title: You: ""We still haven't found the *bullet..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We still haven't found the *bullet*."

fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "You've seen the drawings. You've st..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You've seen the drawings. You've studied them.

fields.Title: Reaction Speed: "He's proposing the bullet was the r..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He's proposing the bullet was the real cause of death -- and the hanging an attempt to *conceal* this fact.

fields.Title: Tutorial Agent: "After you bag the corpse, Lieutenan..."
fields.Dialogue Text: After you bag the corpse, Lieutenant Kitsuragi will leave the party until tomorrow morning. You can do side-tasks and even the main case, but it might be more difficult. Plan his exit accordingly.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I *would* drive him to Processing,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I *would* drive him to Processing, but it's too late to do that today... I'll do it first thing tomorrow. No problem."

fields.Title: You: "Say: "Fuck yeah.""
fields.Dialogue Text: Say: "Fuck yeah."
fields.Alternate1: "This is it."

fields.Title: You: ""There's a cavity... cut right betw..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "There's a cavity... cut right between the hemispheres."
fields.Alternate1: "The cavity is here, cut right between the hemispheres."

fields.Title: The Hanged Man: "Your fingers reach toward his skull..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Your fingers reach toward his skull. His cerebral cortex feels like jelly -- cold jelly -- strange fluid streams down your wrist as you push deeper. Until you feel it, on the tip of your finger...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The bullet falls in the bag leaving..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The bullet falls in the bag leaving a smattering of blood on the plastic. He raises the bag under his eyes and says:

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""And one last thing." *Click-click*..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "And one last thing." *Click-click* goes the pen. "We can now fill in injury #3: ligament mark. Opinion -- non-fatal, post-mortem: *treatment*."
fields.Alternate1: "And one last thing." *Click-click* goes the pen. "We should amend injury #3: ligament mark. *Treatment*. It's obvious the Hardie boys tampered with it."
fields.Alternate2: "This goes very, very well with #3: ligament mark. *Treatment*." *Click-click* goes the pen. "We have the tampering -- and real cause of death. Very neat."
fields.Alternate3: "And one last thing." *Click-click* goes the pen. "We should amend injury #3: ligament mark. New opinion -- non-fatal, post-mortem: *treatment*."

fields.Title: Conceptualization: "This man will never sleep again. Ne..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This man will never sleep again. Never wake.

fields.Title: You: ""Why would anyone do this?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why would anyone do this?"

fields.Title: You: ""Why... yes there was.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why... yes there was."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Klaasje told us the bullet hit him..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Klaasje told us the bullet hit him in the mouth -- try putting your hand there..."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I'll leave that choice to you. And..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'll leave that choice to you. And one more thing..." He looks you in the eye. "Great work, detective."

fields.Title: Authority: "*Detective*."
fields.Dialogue Text: *Detective*.

fields.Title: You: "Say: "Abrasion collar.""
fields.Dialogue Text: Say: "Abrasion collar."

fields.Title: You: ""Agreed.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Agreed."

fields.Title: You: ""Let's hurry then." [Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: "Let's hurry then." [Leave.]

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Okay." He unrolls the plastic. "I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay." He unrolls the plastic. "I need a little help for carrying him to the holding pen of my Kineema. I can take care of the rest."
